    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Apr 11, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-04-11/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Apr 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-04-11/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Patient records left on car roof and scattered in hospital grounds in data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Irish Independent The number of data-protection breaches involving sensitive personal information held by the HSE almost doubled to 212 in 2016. (Stock image).  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.independent.ie/irish-news/health/patient-records-left-on-car-roof-and-scattered-in-hospital-grounds-in-data-breaches-by-hse-35612475.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.independent.ie/irish-news/health/patient-records-left-on-car-roof-and-scattered-in-hospital-grounds-in-data-breaches-by-hse-35612475.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Wonga Data Breach Puts Customer Loyalty at Risk&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An autumn 2016 Thales Group survey probing consumer attitudes about data breaches found relatively few respondents in the UKjust 20%said &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.emarketer.com/Article/Wonga-Data-Breach-Puts-Customer-Loyalty-Risk/1015608&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.emarketer.com/Article/Wonga-Data-Breach-Puts-Customer-Loyalty-Risk/1015608&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Hackers Claim Apple Paid Ransom to Avoid iPhone Wiping&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Members of the cybercriminal outfit provided several technology publications with sample batches of the stolen credentials  many of which were &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://mspmentor.net/mobile-device-management/hackers-claim-apple-paid-ransom-avoid-iphone-wiping&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://mspmentor.net/mobile-device-management/hackers-claim-apple-paid-ransom-avoid-iphone-wiping&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Hospitals to be inspected over handling of patient files&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ms Dixon said the massive data breaches suffered by Yahoo provided a salutary reminder of the sheer quantity of our personal data stored by online &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/hospitals-to-be-inspected-over-handling-of-patient-files-1.3044772&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/hospitals-to-be-inspected-over-handling-of-patient-files-1.3044772&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;2224 data security breaches reported in 2016, says Data Protection&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Siliconrepublic.com Reports of data breaches to see exponential rise once mandatory reporting rules under GDPR come into force, warns Helen Dixon. Ireland&amp;rsquo;s Data &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.siliconrepublic.com/enterprise/data-protection-commissioner-report-2016&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.siliconrepublic.com/enterprise/data-protection-commissioner-report-2016&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Confirming Identity, An Art And Science&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data breaches are so commonplace, might we have become immune to the news of more credentials hacked, more identities stolen? The latest salvo &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.pymnts.com/data-drivers/2017/confirming-identity-an-art-and-science-confirm-bob-geiman-security-and-fraud-digital-identity-verification-innovation-technology/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.pymnts.com/data-drivers/2017/confirming-identity-an-art-and-science-confirm-bob-geiman-security-and-fraud-digital-identity-verification-innovation-technology/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;And Then There Were Two: Closing the Gap on State-Level Data Breach&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lexology (registration) &amp;hellip; into law the 48th state-level data breach notification law, bringing the requirements for notifying individuals affected by data breaches to this state.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.lexology.com/library/detail.aspx?g=9a5efb6f-5de4-48c4-b250-eeed1b0ea5b8&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.lexology.com/library/detail.aspx?g=9a5efb6f-5de4-48c4-b250-eeed1b0ea5b8&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;HHS data shows 1800 large data breaches since 2009&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nearly 1,800 large data breaches involving patient information have occurred since 2009, according to an analysis of publicly available data from the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.healthdatamanagement.com/news/hhs-data-shows-1-800-large-data-breaches-since-2009&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.healthdatamanagement.com/news/hhs-data-shows-1-800-large-data-breaches-since-2009&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data Breach Hits UK Payday Loan Firm Wonga&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The notification process for data breaches will soon be a hot topic, as the EU looks to push through the revised Data Protection directive in May 2018.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.pymnts.com/news/security-and-risk/2017/data-breach-hits-uk-payday-loan-firm-wonga-hack-great-britain-poland-personal-data/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.pymnts.com/news/security-and-risk/2017/data-breach-hits-uk-payday-loan-firm-wonga-hack-great-britain-poland-personal-data/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Erosion of public trust biggest long-term impact of OPM breaches, experts&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;FederalNewsRadio.com &amp;hellip; American public that we can protect that information, he said during an Apr. 10 discussion of the long-term impacts of the OPM data breaches at the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://federalnewsradio.com/opm-cyber-breach/2017/04/erosion-public-trust-biggest-long-term-impact-opm-breaches-experts-say/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://federalnewsradio.com/opm-cyber-breach/2017/04/erosion-public-trust-biggest-long-term-impact-opm-breaches-experts-say/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Irish primary school data held to ransom in cyber attack&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Data Protection Commissioner (DPC) has seen a fall in the number of data breaches reported. During 2016, a total of 2,301 notifications were &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.newstalk.com/Irish-primary-school-data-held-to-ransom-in-cyber-attack&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.newstalk.com/Irish-primary-school-data-held-to-ransom-in-cyber-attack&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Generali Global Assistance Publishes Whitepaper on the Rise of Phishing and&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Marketwired (press release) According to the Identity Theft Resource Center, in 2016, just over 55 percent of the reported 1,093 US data breaches were caused by spearphishing, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/generali-global-assistance-publishes-whitepaper-on-rise-phishing-other-scams-during-2208964.htm&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/generali-global-assistance-publishes-whitepaper-on-rise-phishing-other-scams-during-2208964.htm&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Trend Micro Leverages Newest XGen Security Capabilities in Worry-Free&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Business Wire (press release) DALLAS&amp;ndash;(BUSINESS WIRE)&amp;ndash;Trend Micro Incorporated (TYO: 4704; TSE: 4704), a global leader in cybersecurity solutions, today announced it is &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170411005051/en/Trend-Micro-Leverages-Newest-XGen%E2%84%A2-Security-Capabilities&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170411005051/en/Trend-Micro-Leverages-Newest-XGen%E2%84%A2-Security-Capabilities&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;UK Loan Firm Wonga Suffers Financial Data Breach&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The company is investigating what is &amp;ldquo;looking like one of the biggest&amp;rdquo; data breaches in the country involving financial data. What could be a serious &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/uk-loan-firm-wonga-suffers-financial-data-breach/d/d-id/1328603&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/uk-loan-firm-wonga-suffers-financial-data-breach/d/d-id/1328603&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Report on Yahoo data breach to be delivered in coming weeks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In her report, the commissioner confirmed Yahoo EMEA had reported further data breaches during the investigation that were also in the public &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.irishtimes.com/business/technology/report-on-yahoo-data-breach-to-be-delivered-in-coming-weeks-1.3045386&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.irishtimes.com/business/technology/report-on-yahoo-data-breach-to-be-delivered-in-coming-weeks-1.3045386&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;New report examines the physical security information management (PSIM)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WhaTech This report studies the global Physical Security Information Management (PSIM) market. Learn details of the Analysis, Manufacturing Cost Structure, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.whatech.com/market-research/it/286047-new-report-examines-the-physical-security-information-management-psim-market&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.whatech.com/market-research/it/286047-new-report-examines-the-physical-security-information-management-psim-market&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;UMass Implements Centralized Threat Lifecycle Management Platform&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The LogRhythm platform combines security information and event management, log management, network and endpoint monitoring, user entity and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://campustechnology.com/articles/2017/04/11/umass-implements-centralized-threat-lifecycle-management-platform.aspx&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://campustechnology.com/articles/2017/04/11/umass-implements-centralized-threat-lifecycle-management-platform.aspx&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How Data Breaches can Ruin CX for your Startup&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data breaches affect all the major metrics used to measure CX, including customer satisfaction, Net Promoter Score (NPS), and the Customer Loyalty &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://customerthink.com/how-data-breaches-can-ruin-cx-for-your-startup/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://customerthink.com/how-data-breaches-can-ruin-cx-for-your-startup/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Corporate Counsel Group Issues Law Firm Cyber Guidance&lt;/h3&gt;
